metadata.name: The Burning Carriage
metadata.description:
This is where it all started.
The realization that we are seating ducks on a one-way trip in a burning carriage. 
Sharing our doomed destiny, our inability to control life's circumstances heading straight to the black void of nothingness. 
Fulfilling our master's needs like lambs to the slaughter.
.
We lost the way.
Lost because of Social Networks.
Lost because of Politics.
Lost because of AI.
Lost because of Money.
Lost and lost again.
.
So, is there a way out of this?
Who knows...
But if there is, let's let it all in and accept our reality.
Embrace the fear.
Look into the eyes of the demons.
And say in a sound and clearest of voices...
"We are lost."
.
